{"tid":1458680,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"17/8星期六去北角飲早茶","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T14:45:28.000Z","uid":298978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9664d470bf7a1901759b30fc7c5ba9bf5815bdda","tid":1458680,"uid":298978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:41:34.000Z","msg":"我係p牌但有野想講！<br />\n經過今日散水黨一役，個個都變驚弓之鳥，屌都冇用！我地打唔到林鄭，唔夠黑警打，連和你飛都驚都賴尿！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係，但又<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以比個火熄滅</span></span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地搞唔到頭目就搞爪牙，搞唔到爪牙就搞啲嘍囉！你間北角富臨咁串就搞你先！<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一早入去兩個人坐一枱齋飲唔食野坐全日，冇犯法又有冷氣</span></span>，唔覺意嘈起上黎整爛野又係你蝕！<br />\n多人玩星期日添食，十八區富臨一齊坐，坐都你執粒！反正啲酒樓阿姐多數藍絲！搞到佢地失業一舉兩得！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd2fdce2ca83f87f0815b0d72b8cfb07154f0ae","tid":1458680,"uid":298978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:42:19.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"9b58bd4e7364e3847c29ecd209af5657e0bd479b","tid":1458680,"uid":298978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:42:29.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"bc7b68a2d2fd97a62ade0c16496ac0a56e2fe546","tid":1458680,"uid":298978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:42:39.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"f38998c8845f3b86d157ab802022b2ab5d314123","tid":1458680,"uid":298978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:42:49.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"ad7eedd926e0fa914e9078fa027eb5be0d79b44d","tid":1458680,"uid":298978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:42:59.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"3012e4d999937f6f9147259a73f45a5384c7d6fc","tid":1458680,"uid":298978,"like":0,"dislike"